                <numFillShapes>=<fillArea>squm(<percentTotal>)

                |floating    |total

                ------------------------------------------------------

                M1| 25214= 349610.52 (100.00%)  | 25214= 349610.52

                M2| 27905= 372408.83 (100.00%)  | 27905= 372408.83

                M3| 26106= 348543.27 (100.00%)  | 26106= 348543.27

                M4| 27439= 393704.76 (100.00%)  | 27439= 393704.76

                M5| 24305= 367076.78 (100.00%)  | 24305= 367076.78

